<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后听到一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么声音？” 她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她马上去开门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克跌跌撞撞地走进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32359</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他手里拿着掸子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37436</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“德克！” 王后大喊，“你在干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37436</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克吓了一跳。“我在清扫大门。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43014</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48811</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>王后皱了皱眉。“今天不是清扫的日子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48811</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克的脸变红了。“我只是——”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53100</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“算了。” 国王厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58382</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有麻烦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58382</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>快去叫皇家魔法师来！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63045</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真是的！” 德克小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72538</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆在皇家厨房里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77274</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在练习咒语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克跑了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85664</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89954</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“魔法师！” 他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89954</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93165</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他挥动着掸子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93165</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>掸子上有很多灰尘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“阿嚏！” 汤姆打了个喷嚏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不好了！” 厨师大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106675</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110855</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“灰尘进到汤里了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110855</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114784</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆跑过去帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117542</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117542</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会把灰尘除掉的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124261</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汤姆挥动了魔杖。噗！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124261</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>扑通！德克掉进了水盆里！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“糟了。” 汤姆小声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>猫咪舔了舔爪子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139941</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨师把德克拉出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139941</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145120</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“皇家厨房里不能有灰尘！” 厨师大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145120</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148152</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>德克生气地看着汤姆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151262</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不会放过你的，魔法师！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151262</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是现在你得跟我走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王和王后需要你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
